{"tid":785353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒憂眾志遲早被政府「封艇」","createTime":"2018-08-19T06:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T09:00:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c947c8e3b323c83d2d06bb6871df8d050066d561","tid":785353,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:52:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180819/20479736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F20479736&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5nywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0878f2d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F20479736&h=3a74c113\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180819/20479736</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月19日 <br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒憂眾志遲早被政府「封艇」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180819/large/0818yiu2008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180819%2Flarge%2F0818yiu2008.jpg&h=8a989580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃之鋒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府早前擬以《社團條例》取締主張港獨的香港民族黨，香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒昨出席座談會上指，民主派陣營面對政府「拉人封艇」的情況，香港眾志目前處於「俾人拉咗，但封艇未封到」的狀態，日後被取締是他「意料之內」，料其他青年組織或也不能倖免。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指年輕一代進入「生存戰」<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒昨出席座談會，發言時形容現時年輕一代參與公民社會已進入「生存戰」的狀態，因為面對排山倒海的打壓，年輕人要思考如何生存：「由2014年至今，被理解為青年政治領袖的人，有幾多今日仲係喺公眾嘅注視之下呢？」他指部份人被打壓坐牢、有人退出社運圈、甚至極端至有參與過佔領運動時「捱過警棍」的人，如今投考警察。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒會後補充，預計政府將有針對其他青年組織的行動。他指，由支持香港獨立的學生組織、青年新政、本民前以至香港眾志，日後被政府取締是「意料之內」，眾志會嚴陣以待，例如會先了解政府取締民族黨的理據，然後再部署。黃之鋒指，目前眾志會繼續在組織青年、國際連結等方面工作。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n林正財談內地居住證：防雙重福利<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n昨晚六合彩開獎結果"},{"pid":"cca9397e7f1d7b57a452cde5c46a5d51c7fcca10","tid":785353,"uid":143499,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"又R光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7e3f24ef830310a8499888a02c9ed5ba9bd554","tid":785353,"uid":156121,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"不思進取 不如執柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"2974447ae6036c70a8abc7cfb57e3e11c21b7200","tid":785353,"uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:15:05.000Z","msg":"幾時輪到你<br />\n你搞港獨咩？垃圾"},{"pid":"0890858f33c4fb5eb44fed3da539669ae6a921c0","tid":785353,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"及早成立香港共產黨霸返個位"},{"pid":"ce676dece029bc4f325044b4a2597eaa853dafea","tid":785353,"uid":36820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾， 都無人提你地"},{"pid":"bf2ac1eb7b20f64670afe786c709c4dff6b77afc","tid":785353,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"前排判社會服務令再判囚就香港唔配有黃之鋒(<a href=\"https://lih.kg/afKzgS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/afKzgS</a>)<br />\n而家又轉風向<br />\n點跟好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b985ff6b24295ff8c215a919d27240d2bb735d8c","tid":785353,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:26:34.000Z","msg":"攪地下組織啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976bc097d84678c32215d4d9e5c356b6cf82f843","tid":785353,"uid":60665,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf2ac1eb7b20f64670afe786c709c4dff6b77afc","tid":785353,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"前排判社會服務令再判囚就香港唔配有黃之鋒(<a href=\"https://lih.kg/afKzgS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/afKzgS</a>)<br />\n而家又轉風向<br />\n點跟好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:28:31.000Z","msg":"連登好多五毛"},{"pid":"61803a6d31